# ðŸ”„ Automated Backup Scheduler (Python + AWS S3)

## ðŸ§  Project Overview

This project is an **Infrastructure Automation tool** that automatically creates backups of important files or folders and uploads them to **AWS S3 cloud storage**. It is designed to be lightweight, secure, and suitable for running on a schedule (daily or hourly).

---

## ðŸš€ Features

- ðŸ“¦ Automatically compresses folders into `.zip` archives
- â˜ï¸ Uploads backups to an Amazon S3 bucket
- â° Can be scheduled to run daily or manually triggered
- ðŸ§¾ Retains backup history with timestamps
- ðŸ’¡ AWS Free Tier friendly
- ðŸ” Optional file encryption (via `cryptography`)

